 india is an agriculture country the agriculture has been given full importance by the government since its inception in 2014 soil of  every  field  will  be  examine  to  enrich  it  the  farmers  will  get  insurance  and benefit  in  the  natural  calamity  under  crop  insurance  scheme  the  farmers  are provided big relief on loan interest i think this government is standing in support of farmers and agriculture labours the farmers will get more prices on their crops   